<plot>Set against a dramatic High Seas detective story off the coast of West Africa the international environment group Greenpeace struggles to track down a network of pirate fishing vessels. This one hour documentary shows how rusting Chinese trawlers using slave labor are smuggling their catch in official European Union boxes through the Canary Islands for our supermarkets, shops and restaurants.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?552340</url></doc>
